}}'''''PBA Bowling''''' is a 1982 [[bowling]] sports-based [[video game]] from Mattel Electronics. The game is licensed by the [[Professional Bowlers Association]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newspapers.com/article/the-news/132062669/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20230919171547/https://www.newspapers.com/article/the-news/132062669/|title=Family fun:Intellivision|newspaper=The News|page=54|archivedate=September 19, 2023|date=December 18, 1981|accessdate=September 19, 2023|via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}</ref> and is intended to be played for up to 4 players.<ref name="Joystik"/>

