''[[All Game Guide]]'' gave the game a score of 4 out of 5' stating: "PBA Bowling is a lot of fun if you enjoy the actual sport. Many similarities exist and you have the option of playing pick-up spares if you get tired of the standard game".<ref name="AGG Review"/>

''Joystik Magazine'' praised the game's realistic graphics but criticized the lack of challenging gameplay.<ref name="Joystik">{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/details/joystik_magazine-1982-12/page/n63/mode/2up|title=PBA Bowling|magazine=Joystik|page=62|date=December 1982|accessdate=September 19, 2023}}</ref>

